Good.

512
00:32:30.129 --> 00:32:31.263
What do we say?

513
00:32:33.299 --> 00:32:34.900
Welcome to SAMCRO. boys.

514
00:32:34.901 --> 00:32:36.134
Thank you.

515
00:32:36.135 --> 00:32:38.370
It's great to have Bobby
Elvis back at the table.

516
00:32:41.107 --> 00:32:42.506
Good to be home.

517
00:32:42.507 --> 00:32:46.410
What. did they...
drop the charges on Georgie?

518
00:32:46.411 --> 00:32:49.213
Yeah.
Apparently it was a suicide.

519
00:32:49.214 --> 00:32:51.648
Climbed into the trunk.
shot himself ten times.

520
00:32:56.154 --> 00:32:59.956
I've asked Bobby to be my VP.

521
00:32:59.957 --> 00:33:03.493
What. uh. what about Ope?

522
00:33:03.494 --> 00:33:08.064
I think Ope's gonna have to
step away from the club for awhile.

523
00:33:08.065 --> 00:33:10.633
Too much damage
done to his family.

524
00:33:10.634 --> 00:33:13.836
He's having a hard time not
putting that pain on SAMCRO.

525
00:33:20.076 --> 00:33:21.310
I second Bobby.

526
00:33:21.311 --> 00:33:23.645
Thank you.

527
00:33:23.646 --> 00:33:26.181
Any opposing?

528
00:33:26.182 --> 00:33:27.816
What do we say?

529
00:33:36.558 --> 00:33:38.559
Love you. brother.

530
00:33:46.634 --> 00:33:50.703
I just wanted to say how
happy I am to have a lot of you

531
00:33:50.704 --> 00:33:55.375
back at the table and. uh...
not as much room on my right with

532
00:33:55.376 --> 00:33:58.745
you here. but. uh.
glad you made the cut.

533
00:33:58.746 --> 00:34:00.814
Thanks.

534
00:34:05.986 --> 00:34:11.390
With Opie stepping away.
something I need to tell this club.

535
00:34:11.391 --> 00:34:17.696
It's complicated. so I'm
hoping you hear me out.

536
00:34:17.697 --> 00:34:26.972
Lobo cartel...
did not kill Piney. I did.

537
00:34:38.783 --> 00:34:42.486
Everybody knows that there was no
love lost between Piney and me.

538
00:34:42.487 --> 00:34:47.524
Most of you were witnesses to him
trying to blow my head off in this room.

539
00:34:47.525 --> 00:34:50.360
I went up to the cabin. and I
thought we could maybe work out

540
00:34:50.361 --> 00:34:52.828
this cartel business.

541
00:34:52.829 --> 00:34:57.467
I thought. maybe. me and him. one
on one. cut through the bullshit.

542
00:34:57.468 --> 00:35:01.804
He was a fifth of Patron
deep when I arrived.

543
00:35:01.805 --> 00:35:08.410
I could hardly get out an argument
when he. uh... he drew on me.

544
00:35:08.411 --> 00:35:13.916
I managed to wrestle the
sawed-off out of his hand.

545
00:35:18.822 --> 00:35:20.823
Then he pulled a nine.

546
00:35:23.258 --> 00:35:26.227
I had no choice.

547
00:35:29.097 --> 00:35:34.135
I figured if the. uh. cartel
or the Irish heard that there

548
00:35:34.136 --> 00:35:37.438
was internal beef. that they would
pull the plug on the deal.

549
00:35:37.439 --> 00:35:42.075
so I. uh...
I put it on the Mexicans.

550
00:35:42.076 --> 00:35:45.012
I planned on telling everybody
what went down soon as all the

551
00:35:45.013 --> 00:35:48.582
heat was off but. uh...
Opie found out the truth

552
00:35:48.583 --> 00:35:50.584
before I could do that.

553
00:35:54.555 --> 00:35:55.755
He's the one that shot me.

554
00:35:55.756 --> 00:35:56.522
What?

555
00:35:56.523 --> 00:35:57.222
What?

556
00:36:00.493 --> 00:36:02.562
I lied to Jax.

557
00:36:05.398 --> 00:36:08.133
I told him it was black.

558
00:36:08.134 --> 00:36:10.202
Why'd you lie. man?

559
00:36:14.473 --> 00:36:19.343
You were protecting Ope.

560
00:36:19.344 --> 00:36:20.679
We needed an ambulance.

561
00:36:20.680 --> 00:36:24.415
EMS would report
the bullet wound.

562
00:36:24.416 --> 00:36:27.885
I don't blame Ope
for trying to kill me.

563
00:36:27.886 --> 00:36:31.088
I only wish I could explain
to him what happened.

564
00:36:31.089 --> 00:36:35.960
Anyway... I killed a member.
self-defense or not.

565
00:36:35.961 --> 00:36:39.797
You gotta vote on
whether I stay or go.

566
00:36:43.901 --> 00:36:47.737
We need to live
with this for awhile.

567
00:36:47.738 --> 00:36:51.241
Let's take a day or
two before we vote.

568
00:36:56.247 --> 00:36:58.248
You give me a minute?

569
00:37:21.137 --> 00:37:22.803
What are you doing?

570
00:37:22.804 --> 00:37:27.442
Still a lot of truth I
can't cop to. so... I figured

571
00:37:27.443 --> 00:37:31.879
I would. uh. get out the
rest of what there is.

572
00:37:31.880 --> 00:37:36.383
I'm supposed to believe you're just gonna
throw yourself at the mercy of the club?

573
00:37:36.384 --> 00:37:38.084
Come on. man.

574
00:37:38.085 --> 00:37:40.419
Mea culpas aren't your style.

575
00:37:40.420 --> 00:37:42.488
What's the play?

576
00:37:44.892 --> 00:37:49.029
I'm all out of play.

577
00:37:49.030 --> 00:37:52.565
I'm just trying to do
what's best for SAMCRO.

578
00:37:55.334 --> 00:37:57.770
What's your play. son?

579
00:37:57.771 --> 00:38:05.044
I mean. I get why you stopped Opie. but...
you found out about JT...

580
00:38:10.348 --> 00:38:13.151
How come you didn't kill me?

581
00:38:13.152 --> 00:38:16.420
I need you alive to
keep the Irish happy.

582
00:38:16.421 --> 00:38:19.657
Ah. you never
wanted this cartel deal.

583
00:38:19.658 --> 00:38:23.360
Why would you give a shit
if the Irish are happy?

584
00:38:25.430 --> 00:38:29.132
Just trying to do
what's best for SAMCRO.

585
00:38:29.133 --> 00:38:31.201
Ah.

586
00:38:42.145 --> 00:38:45.047
I just went by the
house to see my grandkids.

587
00:38:45.048 --> 00:38:47.616
Who the hell decided to
put them in day care?

588
00:38:47.617 --> 00:38:49.384
Me and their mother.

589
00:38:50.553 --> 00:38:52.988
We don't let other
people raise our children.

590
00:38:52.989 --> 00:38:54.389
It's selfish and lazy.

591
00:38:54.390 --> 00:38:55.958
I don't have
time for this. Mom.

592
00:38:55.959 --> 00:38:59.994
You want to see the kids.
work it out with Tara.

593
00:39:11.941 --> 00:39:14.808
I still don't
understand. Jackson.

594
00:39:14.809 --> 00:39:16.576
You don't have to.

595
00:39:16.577 --> 00:39:18.645
His time will come.

596
00:39:26.888 --> 00:39:28.188
Hey.

597
00:39:28.189 --> 00:39:29.389
Yeah.

598
00:39:29.390 --> 00:39:31.891
Just making sure
you got home okay.

599
00:39:31.892 --> 00:39:35.061
Oh.

600
00:39:35.062 --> 00:39:37.396
Well. yeah... yeah. I did.

601
00:39:37.397 --> 00:39:38.865
I'm fine.

602
00:39:38.866 --> 00:39:40.566
Good.

603
00:39:40.567 --> 00:39:42.802
So now you have my number.

604
00:39:42.803 --> 00:39:45.704
In case you ever need anything.

605
00:39:45.705 --> 00:39:48.106
Okay.

606
00:39:48.107 --> 00:39:50.575
Thanks.

607
00:40:02.854 --> 00:40:07.491
Weapons...
on the hood of the car.

608
00:40:07.492 --> 00:40:09.026
It's cool.

609
00:40:16.234 --> 00:40:19.535
Mr. Pope has given the
problem some more thought.

610
00:40:19.536 --> 00:40:25.041
and he realizes nothing the Sons
offer is gonna be good enough.

611
00:40:25.042 --> 00:40:29.245
But you...
get to give 'em your message.

612
00:40:29.246 --> 00:40:32.115
What am I supposed
to do with this?

613
00:40:32.116 --> 00:40:33.549
Kill Teller.

614
00:40:52.367 --> 00:40:54.501
I thought this
meeting was with Pope?

615
00:40:54.502 --> 00:40:58.039
<i>Mr.</i> Pope would like
this discussion to happen first.

616
00:40:58.040 --> 00:40:59.874
I'm his associate.
August Marks.

617
00:40:59.875 --> 00:41:01.675
Weapons.

618
00:41:22.863 --> 00:41:25.130
Gotta settle
things with the Niners.

619
00:41:25.131 --> 00:41:27.366
Where the hell's Laroy?

620
00:41:27.367 --> 00:41:31.136
Darnell's in charge now.

621
00:41:31.137 --> 00:41:32.537
Work it out.

622
00:41:34.741 --> 00:41:36.342
Hey.

623
00:41:41.313 --> 00:41:44.883
Look. man. we got a lot of
history with your crew.

624
00:41:44.884 --> 00:41:48.786
We've beefed before. both made
mistakes. but we get through it.

625
00:41:48.787 --> 00:41:51.155
Just tell me what you need.

626
00:42:03.968 --> 00:42:04.834
Drop him. Darnell!

627
00:42:04.835 --> 00:42:06.403
Go. Jackie. boy!

628
00:42:06.404 --> 00:42:07.905
We'll get back at
these bastards!

629
00:42:07.906 --> 00:42:09.406
Kill. Jackie!

630
00:42:09.407 --> 00:42:11.507
Come on. D. get up. man!

631
00:42:11.508 --> 00:42:12.942
That's enough.

632
00:42:12.943 --> 00:42:13.709
That's enough!

633
00:42:13.710 --> 00:42:14.476
Jax!

634
00:42:14.477 --> 00:42:16.445
JJ! Jackie boy!

635
00:42:18.815 --> 00:42:20.516
I thought you pulled weapons?

636
00:42:20.517 --> 00:42:25.087
I did.

637
00:42:25.088 --> 00:42:26.254
Jesus Christ.

638
00:42:26.255 --> 00:42:29.424
He didn't really
want to be in charge anyway.

639
00:42:29.425 --> 00:42:30.725
You. what's your name?

640
00:42:30.726 --> 00:42:32.727
TYLER Ty... T-Tyler.

641
00:42:32.728 --> 00:42:35.630
Well. T-T Tyler.
you need to go back to

642
00:42:35.631 --> 00:42:39.067
your crew and tell 'em the
beef with the Sons is done.

643
00:42:39.068 --> 00:42:42.102
If it continues. so will the
turnover in leadership.

644
00:42:42.103 --> 00:42:44.138
There ain't nothing to think over.
Go!

645
00:42:44.139 --> 00:42:45.439
Yeah. all right.

646
00:42:45.440 --> 00:42:46.440
Well. go!

647
00:42:46.441 --> 00:42:48.242
All right.

648
00:42:51.346 --> 00:42:55.349
What the hell is this?

649
00:42:55.350 --> 00:42:59.285
Mr. Pope will
reach out to you soon.

650
00:42:59.286 --> 00:43:02.021
Dump him!

651
00:43:02.022 --> 00:43:05.891
This is Pope letting us know...
he's the one who

652
00:43:05.892 --> 00:43:07.860
decides who lives and dies.

653
00:43:19.673 --> 00:43:22.775
I think that's the last of it.

654
00:43:24.945 --> 00:43:26.278
Showerhead's leaking.

655
00:43:26.279 --> 00:43:29.147
I'll have Chucky come by
tomorrow and change the washers.

656
00:43:29.148 --> 00:43:30.648
Thanks.

657
00:43:32.952 --> 00:43:37.555
I know how hard it
was to admit that today.

658
00:43:37.556 --> 00:43:41.092
I'm glad you came clean.

659
00:43:41.093 --> 00:43:43.427
No one's gonna vote you out.

660
00:43:43.428 --> 00:43:47.197
It's out of my
shaky little hands.

661
00:43:54.105 --> 00:43:55.338
Hey.

662
00:43:58.175 --> 00:44:00.577
I'm good. Thanks.

663
00:44:23.332 --> 00:44:30.204
I. uh... murdered...
an innocent girl.

664
00:44:30.205 --> 00:44:35.876
The lie was to protect
Ope and the club. not me.

665
00:44:35.877 --> 00:44:42.182
I was with you...
in the hospital... every day...

666
00:44:42.183 --> 00:44:46.854
for three weeks.

667
00:44:46.855 --> 00:44:49.523
You should've told
me the truth. Clay.

668
00:44:51.992 --> 00:44:55.294
I didn't know how.

669
00:44:55.295 --> 00:44:58.831
Sorry.

670
00:45:09.075 --> 00:45:13.278
Yeah?

671
00:45:13.279 --> 00:45:15.480
Shit.

672
00:45:15.481 --> 00:45:18.784
Where?

673
00:45:18.785 --> 00:45:21.553
No. I'll come and get her.

674
00:45:21.554 --> 00:45:24.589
No. Yeah.

675
00:45:24.590 --> 00:45:29.260
Yeah. all right. Yeah. thanks.

676
00:45:29.261 --> 00:45:31.563
What's that?

677
00:45:31.564 --> 00:45:35.400
Oakland detective
stopped Dawn for DUI.

678
00:45:35.401 --> 00:45:37.935
His. uh. brother-in-law's
a Grim Bastard.

679
00:45:37.936 --> 00:45:41.738
But if I pick her up myself.
they won't charge her.

680
00:45:50.948 --> 00:45:52.616
We good?

681
00:45:56.152 --> 00:45:57.886
I don't know.

682
00:46:08.832 --> 00:46:10.298
Uh-huh?

683
00:46:10.299 --> 00:46:14.469
LT. these two girls
came in. said they witnessed

684
00:46:14.470 --> 00:46:19.073
guys on motorcycles shooting
a black man in an SUV.

685
00:46:19.074 --> 00:46:20.875
Picked out Teller and Chibs.

686
00:46:24.947 --> 00:46:26.714
Oakland PD just called.

687
00:46:26.715 --> 00:46:29.916
Another two witnesses came in.
identified Tig Trager as the guy

688
00:46:29.917 --> 00:46:32.486
that ran down Veronica Pope.

689
00:46:49.770 --> 00:46:52.472
Detective Goodman. Oakland PD.

690
00:46:52.473 --> 00:46:53.273
You Trager?

691
00:46:53.274 --> 00:46:56.175
Yeah. Where's Dawn?

692
00:46:56.176 --> 00:46:58.810
Hands on your head.

693
00:46:58.811 --> 00:47:01.246
Shit. man. you
gotta be kidding me.

694
00:47:01.247 --> 00:47:03.749
Do it!

695
00:47:17.963 --> 00:47:19.197
Walk.

696
00:47:19.198 --> 00:47:20.298
No. man.

697
00:47:20.299 --> 00:47:23.134
- I'm not going anywhere until...
- Shut up!

698
00:47:25.971 --> 00:47:27.672
Move.

699
00:47:52.495 --> 00:47:54.462
Oh. goddamn it.

700
00:47:58.701 --> 00:48:03.138
Do you know who
I am. Mr. Trager?

701
00:48:03.139 --> 00:48:05.106
Yeah.

702
00:48:05.107 --> 00:48:08.009
And do you know
what happens now?

703
00:48:08.010 --> 00:48:10.277
You kill me.

704
00:48:10.278 --> 00:48:12.980
That'd be too easy.

705
00:48:30.998 --> 00:48:34.500
Oh. no. Oh. no.

706
00:48:34.501 --> 00:48:37.536
Dawny?

707
00:48:37.537 --> 00:48:41.640
Dawny. hey. Dawn.

708
00:48:41.641 --> 00:48:43.709
Baby?

709
00:48:43.710 --> 00:48:55.788
Oh. baby... Wake up! Oh. man...
Oh. shit! No. baby... No! No!

710
00:48:55.789 --> 00:48:57.456
Hey. baby!

711
00:48:57.457 --> 00:49:00.324
Oh. baby. oh... Stop! Oh. baby!

712
00:49:00.325 --> 00:49:01.526
Daddy?

713
00:49:01.527 --> 00:49:03.495
I'm so sorry. baby.

714
00:49:03.496 --> 00:49:05.530
Oh. oh. baby...

715
00:49:05.531 --> 00:49:07.599
Let me go! No!

716
00:49:07.600 --> 00:49:09.033
What's happening?

717
00:49:09.034 --> 00:49:10.735
Goddamn it!

718
00:49:10.736 --> 00:49:13.505
Let me go! Let me go!

719
00:49:13.506 --> 00:49:15.873
Daddy. get me out of here!

720
00:49:15.874 --> 00:49:19.175
Oh. baby...

721
00:49:19.176 --> 00:49:21.912
Oh. man. I'm sorry.

722
00:49:21.913 --> 00:49:23.947
Please... please. not her.

723
00:49:23.948 --> 00:49:25.549
Kill me. Please. I beg you.

724
00:49:25.550 --> 00:49:28.652
Please. kill me. please?

725
00:49:28.653 --> 00:49:29.319
Please?

726
00:49:29.320 --> 00:49:32.254
Know my pain. Mr. Trager.

727
00:49:39.129 --> 00:49:43.699
Oh. baby... Oh. no!

728
00:49:43.700 --> 00:49:45.367
No!

729
00:49:50.940 --> 00:49:51.873
Daddy!

730
00:50:00.882 --> 00:50:03.250
Mr. Trager. you and some
of your crew have been ID'd

731
00:50:03.251 --> 00:50:06.819
for the murder of my daughter
and the highway shooting.

732
00:50:06.820 --> 00:50:13.092
Detective Goodman will
take you to County.

733
00:50:13.093 --> 00:50:18.331
You should keep this vivid
memory to yourself.

734
00:50:18.332 --> 00:50:23.235
I'd hate to see the same thing
happen to your other daughter.

735
00:50:23.236 --> 00:50:25.537
I am gonna cut your
ugly. black head off.

736
00:50:36.382 --> 00:50:38.750
Get your cleaner out here.

737
00:50:38.751 --> 00:50:41.886
You got it.

738
00:50:45.791 --> 00:50:48.993
Let's go.

739
00:50:59.203 --> 00:51:00.704
Thomas is congested.

740
00:51:00.705 --> 00:51:03.307
Need a humidifier in that room.

741
00:51:03.308 --> 00:51:04.441
It's not a dry cough.

742
00:51:04.442 --> 00:51:07.443
A humidifier won't help.

743
00:51:10.447 --> 00:51:13.015
And they don't
need to be in day care.

744
00:51:13.016 --> 00:51:14.417
We can take care of our own.

745
00:51:14.418 --> 00:51:20.556
They need to socialize
with other children.

746
00:51:20.557 --> 00:51:27.028
And let's be honest...
I don't think you're up for the task.

747
00:51:27.029 --> 00:51:28.029
Excuse me?

748
00:51:28.030 --> 00:51:30.131
You have every right to
be distracted. you've been

749
00:51:30.132 --> 00:51:33.702
- through a lot...
- Just say what you mean.

750
00:51:33.703 --> 00:51:41.274
I smell weed and alcohol
on your breath every morning.

751
00:51:41.275 --> 00:51:45.278
I don't smoke or
drink in the morning.

752
00:51:45.279 --> 00:51:46.913
I'm a doctor. Gemma.

753
00:51:46.914 --> 00:51:49.249
I know how long drugs and
alcohol stay in your system.

754
00:51:49.250 --> 00:51:55.588
And until you... you pull it together.
I don't want you alone with my boys.

755
00:51:55.589 --> 00:51:59.425
Really.

756
00:51:59.426 --> 00:52:01.961
Jax feel the same way?

757
00:52:01.962 --> 00:52:06.399
I didn't tell him. but
he knows you're not yourself.

758
00:52:09.236 --> 00:52:10.770
Hey. baby.

759
00:52:10.771 --> 00:52:13.304
Hey.

760
00:52:13.305 --> 00:52:15.173
I knew you'd be here.

761
00:52:15.174 --> 00:52:16.174
Hello. my love.

762
00:52:16.175 --> 00:52:18.176
Welcome home. sweetheart.

763
00:52:18.177 --> 00:52:20.178
Oh. I'm glad you're out.

764
00:52:20.179 --> 00:52:21.946
Bobby wanted to see the boys.

765
00:52:21.947 --> 00:52:23.882
Oh. they just went down.

766
00:52:23.883 --> 00:52:26.951
Go ahead.

767
00:52:30.455 --> 00:52:32.423
We okay?

768
00:52:32.424 --> 00:52:34.859
Oh. yeah.

769
00:52:34.860 --> 00:52:36.293
We're perfect.

770
00:52:42.333 --> 00:52:43.600
Hey.

771
00:52:43.601 --> 00:52:45.268
Hey. uh. Gemma.

772
00:52:45.269 --> 00:52:46.369
I need Jax.

773
00:52:46.370 --> 00:52:47.370
Why?

774
00:52:47.371 --> 00:52:50.540
